author: CBR
description:
In this Doctor Strange vs Pennywise matchup, we compare the Sorcerer Supreme’s spell arsenal to IT’s fear-fueled powers and reveal who would be the ultimate winner.

Strange’s training at Kamar-Taj, the Vishanti, Shields and Bands, illusions, telepathy, astral projection, teleportation, and time tricks vs Pennywise’s shapeshifting, deadlights, psionics, and Derry-bound influence. We lay out the do-or-die strategy—bind, banish, or the Ritual of Chud—and decide the winner.

Chapters
00:00 – Setup: Why This Crossover Fight Matters
00:12 – Doctor Strange: Origin and Training
01:17 – Doctor Strange’s Powers, Spells and Artifacts
08:01 – Doctor Strange’s Limits and Weaknesses
09:00 – Pennywise: True Nature and Abilities
12:04 – Pennywise’s Strengths and Weaknesses
12:54 – Battle Breakdown and Verdict
